HEADWORD: In posse
<hw>In` pos"se</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>In
possibility; possible, although not yet in existence or come to pass; --
contradistinguished from <contr>in esse</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

